BRIef           %BBri%Oef%I%I       114   1
Chat            %BC%Ohat%I%I         33   1
COOKIE          %BCookie%O%I%I      105   1
Download        %BD%Oownload%I       37  10
ECHO            %BEcho%O%I%I         22   1
Empfangen       %BE%Ompfangen%I      37  10
